title: Shred With Tim Humphreys & Neff Outerwear
description: Tim Humphreys takes you on an awesome shredding journey while rocking the new line of Neff Outerwear. From backwoods, to mountains, to parks, experience the full spectrum of Tim's snowboarding. The New Jersey native shows his love for the backcountry as well as the park. He has publicly spoken out about his views on competition riding. He believes that the constant pursuit of progression such as new tricks and pushing the limit can compromise style. He believes that style embodies the true beauty of the sport. However, he has said that Winter X is a perfect bridge between the core rider and the mainstream. So make sure to check out Neff rider Tim Humphreys out at Winter X.
